sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Operator
    participant Job as LMEval Job Container<br/>(lmes-job)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Operator,Job: Flow 1: Online Benchmark Evaluation

    Operator->>Job: Create Kubernetes Job<br/>Mount /meta/job.json + secrets
    activate Job

    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: INITIALIZING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Job->>HF: GET datasets & tokenizers<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (optional)
    HF-->>Job: Dataset files + tokenizer

    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: LOADING_DATA
    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: RUNNING_EVALUATION

    loop For each evaluation batch
        Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)<br/>Batched prompts (num_concurrent)
        Model-->>Job: Completions response
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: POST_PROCESSING

    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS
    Job->>OCI: skopeo push<br/>Auth: Docker config.json<br/>Evaluation results as OCI artifact
    OCI-->>Job: Push confirmed

    opt MLflow enabled
        Job->>MLflow: POST metrics & results<br/>Auth: via EvalHub SDK
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: COMPLETED<br/>Final scored results
    deactivate Job

    Note over Operator,Job: Flow 2: Air-Gapped / Offline Evaluation

    Operator->>Job: Create Job with /test_data volume<br/>(pre-populated by init container)
    activate Job

    Note over Job: Auto-detect /test_data<br/>Set HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1

    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: INITIALIZING

    Note over Job: Load datasets from /test_data<br/>(no HuggingFace Hub calls)

    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: RUNNING_EVALUATION

    loop For each evaluation batch
        Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>Custom CA cert supported
        Model-->>Job: Completions response
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: COMPLETED<br/>Final scored results
    deactivate Job
